  "message": "test(e2e): add phase-1 matrix validation coverage to CI gate and QA policy tests\n\nUpdate CI full suite gate and QA docs policy validation tests to verify that\nthe phase-1 matrix validation artifact is properly wired into the evidence\ncontract:\n\nci_full_suite_gate.rs:\n- run_all_wires_scenario_cell_status_artifacts_into_evidence_contract now\n  checks for PERF_PHASE1_MATRIX_VALIDATION_JSON env var, phase1_matrix_validation.json\n  artifact path, and the three claim_integrity check IDs (phase1_matrix_validation_json,\n  phase1_matrix_validation_schema, phase1_matrix_correlation_matches_run)\n\nqa_docs_policy_validation.rs:\n- run_all_claim_integrity_gate_wires_fail_closed_conditions adds the three\n  new phase1 matrix check IDs and realistic_session_shape_coverage to the\n  required fail-closed conditions list\n- run_all_emits_scenario_cell_status_artifacts now checks for\n  realistic_session_shape_coverage, source, and source_path fields in\n  scenario cell status output\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
